{"tid":1632364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊拉克連日反政府示威　兩電視台遇襲損毀嚴重","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:38:10.000Z","uid":51620,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"124dad55a77bc2a6669198cead5a8016f0912ac8","tid":1632364,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:20.000Z","msg":"伊拉克連日反政府示威　兩電視台遇襲損毀嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=365333&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365333%26refer%3DShare&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpqbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=717bb8bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365333%26refer%3DShare&h=fe7f92b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=365333&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】伊拉克首都巴格達經歷連日反政府示威者，周日局勢稍為平靜，但當地有兩間電視台遇襲，設施遭到嚴重破壞。<br />\n<br />\n遇襲的兩間私人電視台設施嚴重損毀，除了衛星直播車，辦公室及錄影廠亦被破壞。<br />\n<br />\n電視台表示，一批穿着黑衫的蒙面襲擊者到電視台大肆破壞，批評總理邁赫迪施政不力，令當地無法無天。<br />\n<br />\n巴格達之前數天發生反政府示威，造成超過90人死亡，近四千人受傷。當地局勢周日較為平靜，但不少商店仍然關閉，街道有不少軍警駐守。<br />\n<br />\n伊拉克國會舉行緊急會議商討局勢。總理邁赫迪表示，他願意與示威者會面，聆聽他們的訴求，但同時呼籲暫停示威。"},{"pid":"3cd00671ff12228ba0a28cfe5587bb90f2854252","tid":1632364,"uid":39796,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"太暴力了<br />\n畫面唔靚"},{"pid":"175b2054f6fb6d6eb34f452e9505c440dd4ab8ad","tid":1632364,"uid":258409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"暫時只有CCTVB俾義務交通督導員截過同埋今日雞尾酒甩手中記者，其他全部都係POPO搞"},{"pid":"879a780663ed411af4ccdde0efe7d6e19ec5c8be","tid":1632364,"uid":51620,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3cd00671ff12228ba0a28cfe5587bb90f2854252","tid":1632364,"uid":39796,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"太暴力了<br />\n畫面唔靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:56:08.000Z","msg":"但我覺得好靚"},{"pid":"597a5ac1baba4d29f91ce78de1c43cecd7afae8b","tid":1632364,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"大家想像下紅底01同tvb比人郁<br />\n成個觀感就好爽"},{"pid":"519da3f399e01089466a8a127945661dc5ec21d2","tid":1632364,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"要搞清楚嗰兩間電視台係 撐政府定 示威者<br />\n<br />\n如果撐示威者就係政府做"},{"pid":"012b0ff80d5b360786be7157541825ca5db3c76c","tid":1632364,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"超過90人死亡<br />\n<br />\n我唔想見到再有手足俾黑警打死"},{"pid":"9694497205433f59c62bffe5189266b756e57b3c","tid":1632364,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e162317e6a430f11fee912e1eac23cfefb449b","tid":1632364,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"將軍澳裝修師傅又有job接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dadabc9d590a45ba295aedd337202aa24b6b0f","tid":1632364,"uid":76690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:51.000Z","msg":"琴日先有人開post話裝修tbb 比成班on9屌到仆街"},{"pid":"2d3db8fef1a2ebb8a3e0d92923df0eec2582e7fb","tid":1632364,"uid":195998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3cd00671ff12228ba0a28cfe5587bb90f2854252","tid":1632364,"uid":39796,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"太暴力了<br />\n畫面唔靚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"失民意 ！！<br />\n<br />\n民意逆轉 ！！<br />\n<br />\n等睇美帝射兩粒核彈教訓示威者"},{"pid":"6275f838e671de82736e5ba98ae4aa3b8cba268c","tid":1632364,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d3db8fef1a2ebb8a3e0d92923df0eec2582e7fb","tid":1632364,"uid":195998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pi